- PWA install: capture beforeinstallprompt and surface an 'Install the
  app' button in Group settings (iOS gets Add-to-Home-Screen guidance);
  hidden when already standalone
- Invite + new 'Share status' use the native share sheet when available,
  clipboard fallback otherwise; share-status copy leads with how many
  swaps are waiting for the group (viral loop)
